      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <ol class="- topic/ol ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">In the HU250 interface navigate to <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Maintenance &gt; Advanced &gt; IP configuration</uicontrol>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Select <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Device &gt; WAN</uicontrol>.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p "> Here you can view and change the IP settings for the WAN ports
(<b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ETH1</b> and <b translate="no" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">ETH2</b>).</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">Click the <uicontrol translate="no" class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol> button
to apply any changes.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The default settings for WAN is fixed address with:<sl class="- topic/sl ">
               <sli class="- topic/sli ">
                  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">IP:</b>
                  <ph platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">159.215.153.100</ph>
                  <ph platform="Modular-DC Modular-Inverter Modular-AC"
                      translate="no"
                      class="- topic/ph ">10.10.10.11</ph>
               </sli>
               <sli class="- topic/sli ">
                  <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Subnet Mask:</b>
                  <ph translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">255.255.255.0</ph>
               </sli>
            </sl>
         </p>
         <note type="important" class="- topic/note ">The default <ph platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">NMC</ph>
            <ph platform="Modular-DC Modular-Inverter Modular-AC"
                translate="no"
                class="- topic/ph ">Reality
Modular</ph> IP address is <ph platform="PXP PxW WxW SDC" translate="no" class="- topic/ph ">159.215.153.93</ph>
            <ph platform="Modular-DC Modular-Inverter Modular-AC"
                translate="no"
                class="- topic/ph ">10.10.10.10</ph>. If the default IP is not used, please check the IP settings and
specify a suitable WAN address accordingly.</note>
